snippet.title: Red Dead Redemption 2: Official Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
Captured entirely from in-game footage, watch this introduction to Red Dead Redemption 2's gameplay in 4K.

Red Dead Redemption 2 is coming October 26, 2018 to PlayStation 4 and Xbox One systems. Pre-order now at rockstargames.com/reddeadredemption2/order
